snippet.title: Space Pricks - Chapter One: Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Space Pricks is an Asteroids-style shoot-em-up-meets-RPG that's inspired by true events.  Download now and join a quest to defeat the biggest PRICKS in the universe: UPPER MANAGEMENT.

Space Pricks - Chapter One is available to download over on Itch!  Nab Chapter One for free now at: https://conorogames.itch.io/space-pricks

Follow me on Itch or Twitter for development updates.
Itch: https://conorogames.itch.io/
Twitter: @ConoroGames
